{
  "stem": "18520.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 351.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother and my sister that is older from me two years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Gershon is--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a brother that he was two or three years younger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hershl and me-- five people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We saw in the beginning-- when we-- the way this was handled-- took us on trucks, not prepare the people to walk up and sit down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like they said, you are going to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and then we got to do the-- where the cargo was there-- the-- the-- the-- the train or whatever, and this is-- the openings of those trains is very high-- the floor.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's this high.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All people-- woman, the heavy people-- couldn't walk up, couldn't jump up to here and then pull yourself in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the same time, you had the whole length-- I don't know how many-- this-- what do you call this?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Each segment-- each-- each--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The cars.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This cars-- those cars, when you didn't see an end of it-- and everybody-- old women, people-- they cannot go in-- nothing to walk on to go on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they're screaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans screaming the whole length-- you [GERMAN], you-- you-- you [GERMAN] with this, with that, you know, all kind of this.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They make you right away low, nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're not worth anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what happened was that we had to pull everybody up and help each other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they filled it up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't-- in those cargo-- they filled it up with I don't know how many people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You were sitting, like-- packed each other close.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, and then they locked it-- locked it, and it was just an opening there with a little screen on top in both ends.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'll tell you something.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
